al enemies on you becomes weaker and weaker. Othe=\r\nrs may or may not be able to see and judge your progress, but you know your=\r\n progress and weaknesses the best. THAT is the crux and siddhis have no rel=\r\nevance or meaning. Any fascination for them will set you back in your sadha=\r\nna. &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 =\r\nface=3DVerdana&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;&nbsp; &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT c=\r\nolor=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;Best regards, &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;=\r\n/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I=\r\n&gt;Narasimha &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 si=\r\nze=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;-----------------------------------------------=\r\n-------------------- &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D=\r\n#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;&nbsp; Free Jyotish Software, Free Jy=\r\notish Lessons, Jyotish Writings, &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;F=\r\nONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual m=\r\nanuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana: &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=\r\n=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb=\r\nsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; http://www.VedicAstrologer.org &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV alig=\r\nn=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&n=\r\nbsp;&nbsp; Films that make a difference: http://SaraswatiFilms.org &lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt;=\r\n&lt;/FONT&gt;